+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WV3Gah1UoXTpLxW596e1Hb","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Phase 9: Progress Tracking and Cancellation\n     2→\n     3→Add the ability to report progress on running tasks and to cancel tasks.\n     4→\n     5→## Requirements\n     6→\n     7→- A processing task can report its progress as a percentage (0-100) with an optional message.\n     8→- There should be a way to query a task's current progress.\n     9→- Listeners can subscribe to progress updates for a task and receive notifications when progress changes.\n    10→- Subscriptions should be cancellable (unsubscribe).\n    11→- Tasks in pending or processing state can be cancelled.\n    12→- Cancelled pending tasks are removed from the queue and will not be returned.\n    13→- Cancelled processing tasks have their status updated accordingly.\n    14→- Cancelled tasks are never retried, even if they had retries remaining.\n    15→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"93205308-0ac7-4030-a926-966870070e57","uuid":"c4de0a06-a789-4be4-a1fe-a3420c3aee0e","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/phases/phase-09.md","content":"# Phase 9: Progress Tracking and Cancellation\n\nAdd the ability to report progress on running tasks and to cancel tasks.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- A processing task can report its progress as a percentage (0-100) with an optional message.\n- There should be a way to query a task's current progress.\n- Listeners can subscribe to progress updates for a task and receive notifications when progress changes.\n- Subscriptions should be cancellable (unsubscribe).\n- Tasks in pending or processing state can be cancelled.\n- Cancelled pending tasks are removed from the queue and will not be returned.\n- Cancelled processing tasks have their status updated accordingly.\n- Cancelled tasks are never retried, even if they had retries remaining.\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":15}}}
